265
00:25:38,720 --> 00:25:44,780
I hope the sight of it will bring solace to you in the Mortal Realm, Your Majesty.

266
00:25:50,900 --> 00:25:52,420
All right.

267
00:25:53,460 --> 00:25:55,500
I'll keep it.

268
00:25:55,500 --> 00:26:01,680
Your Majesty, you refuse to take our offerings, but you treasure that mere seed.

269
00:26:01,680 --> 00:26:05,480
Does the seed have some other significance?

270
00:26:06,800 --> 00:26:10,340
