276
00:26:41,180 --> 00:26:45,860
Since her memory was forcefully removed, she can only be a demon now.

277
00:26:45,860 --> 00:26:47,580
A demon?

278
00:26:49,760 --> 00:26:52,680
That's not bad. They live a long life.

279
00:26:52,680 --> 00:26:56,940
