325
00:31:16,200 --> 00:31:17,200
Let me go.

326
00:31:17,200 --> 00:31:18,400
I won’t!

327
00:31:18,400 --> 00:31:20,600
I won't kill myself.

328
00:31:20,600 --> 00:31:23,720
I'll be the Mountain Chief, all right?

329
00:31:40,520 --> 00:31:45,000
The mark on my wrist was left by the person I'm looking for.

330
00:31:45,000 --> 00:31:52,100
I'm using a spell to combine my blood and her spiritual power.

331
00:31:52,100 --> 00:31:57,620
Fish will gather here, pick up her scent,

332
00:31:57,620 --> 00:32:01,740
swim along the current, and track her down.

333
00:32:02,880 --> 00:32:04,820
The world is vast.

334
00:32:04,820 --> 00:32:07,900
How much blood do you have to drain to find her?

335
00:32:08,980 --> 00:32:12,280
I don't like your self-harming way of finding someone.

336
00:32:13,180 --> 00:32:15,140
Let's find another solution.

337
00:32:15,140 --> 00:32:20,340
I would do anything to find her.

338
00:32:24,960 --> 00:32:26,680
How romantic of you.

339
00:32:26,680 --> 00:32:30,620
The person you're looking for must be a demon.

340
00:33:00,480 --> 00:33:02,720
What is this?

341
00:33:02,720 --> 00:33:04,440
What's going on?

342
00:33:04,440 --> 00:33:06,000
No way.

343
00:33:06,000 --> 00:33:08,720
Did I work too much these two days?

344
00:33:12,200 --> 00:33:13,580
Oh, no!

345
00:33:13,580 --> 00:33:17,740
It is already bad enough that I lost my memories at such a young age.

346
00:33:17,740 --> 00:33:20,640
And now I'm becoming ugly?

347
00:33:32,840 --> 00:33:35,440
A fish with a pink mark?

348
00:33:36,180 --> 00:33:40,960
Maybe Heaven heard my plea and sent me the solution.

349
00:33:50,780 --> 00:33:53,600
As they say, "Eat the part to cure the part."

350
00:33:53,600 --> 00:33:57,320
After I ate this fish, my beauty has been restored!

351
00:33:58,780 --> 00:34:01,720
No. I have to get more of them.

352
00:34:12,060 --> 00:34:14,260
Why would that old man want to attack me with a wooden sword?

353
00:34:14,260 --> 00:34:16,600
Was the fish his pet?

354
00:34:17,580 --> 00:34:19,560
Mister...

355
00:34:20,360 --> 00:34:22,480
I should run.

356
00:34:23,660 --> 00:34:25,300
The Southern Capital is populated.

357
00:34:25,300 --> 00:34:27,240
This demon is using her power recklessly.

358
00:34:27,240 --> 00:34:30,360
She might frighten the mortals.

359
00:34:39,000 --> 00:34:41,500
Seriously? It was just one fish. No need to chase me like that.

360
00:34:41,500 --> 00:34:43,980
Does he have to make a big deal out of this?

361
00:35:08,520 --> 00:35:13,300
This demon is weak but smart.

362
00:35:15,900 --> 00:35:22,240
   

363
00:35:22,240 --> 00:35:26,540
Fairy Zhi Xi, are you in charge of this year's divine tool replacement for all palaces?

364
00:35:26,540 --> 00:35:29,540
Fairy Ying Deng is about to be promoted to be His Supreme Majesty's assistant.

365
00:35:29,540 --> 00:35:34,540
She has a lot on her plate, so she entrusts trivial matters to me.

366
00:35:35,960 --> 00:35:41,780
In that case, you'll be the curator once she leaves.

