368
00:35:44,340 --> 00:35:47,040
It's time for a change in ranks.

369
00:35:47,740 --> 00:35:51,900
Indeed. It is time.

370
00:36:17,100 --> 00:36:21,120
Your Supreme Majesty, fellow deities,

371
00:36:21,120 --> 00:36:25,480
I am Ying Deng, Curator of Magical Pavilion.

372
00:36:25,480 --> 00:36:29,100
The bicentennial replacement of divine tools,

373
00:36:29,100 --> 00:36:35,640
