374
00:36:35,640 --> 00:36:38,940
Since I'm about to leave the Pavilion,

375
00:36:38,940 --> 00:36:44,100
I fear that my successor will mess things up due to her lack of experience.

376
00:36:44,100 --> 00:36:50,080
Therefore, before I step down, I have prepared new divine tools for all of you.

377
00:36:50,080 --> 00:36:53,240
I appreciate your efforts, Fairy Ying Deng.

378
00:37:31,900 --> 00:37:33,900
What a delicate object.

379
00:37:33,900 --> 00:37:35,980
What is that divine tool?

380
00:37:42,060 --> 00:37:47,200
Your Supreme Majesty, that is the artifact I prepared for Emperor Ying Yuan.

381
00:37:47,200 --> 00:37:48,660
He is going through the trials in Mortal Realm.

382
00:37:48,660 --> 00:37:51,380
He'll be able to use it when he returns.

383
00:37:51,380 --> 00:37:52,600
Good.

384
00:37:52,600 --> 00:37:56,220
I'm glad you served him in Yanxu Heavenly Palace.

385
00:37:56,220 --> 00:37:57,860
Bring it here.

386
