00:39:15,620 --> 00:39:19,520
Your Supreme Majesty, Curator Ying Deng has always been attentive to His Majesty's well-being.

396
00:39:19,520 --> 00:39:23,320
She is very meticulous too, so she would never make such a simple mistake.

397
00:39:23,320 --> 00:39:27,020
I think someone might have stolen the jade buckle.

398
00:39:34,440 --> 00:39:36,140
